---
// BetaModal.astro
---
<div id="beta-modal-overlay" class="modal-overlay hidden">
    <div class="modal-card beta-card">
        <div class="beta-icon">
            <svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"></path>
                <line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"></line>
                <line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"></line>
            </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="beta-content">
            <h2>Función en fase Beta</h2>
            <p>La sección de <strong>Llamadas y Calendario</strong> se encuentra actualmente en desarrollo activo.</p>
            <p>Estamos trabajando para ofrecerte una experiencia P2P completa. Algunas funciones pueden ser inestables o estar limitadas temporalmente.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="beta-actions">
            <button id="btn-beta-close" class="apple-button primary">Entendido</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .modal-overlay {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
        background: rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px) saturate(150%);
        z-index: 6000;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease-out;
    }
    @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; } to { opacity: 1; } }

    .beta-card {
        background: #FFFFFF;
        width: 400px;
        padding: 32px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        animation: slideInUp 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.1, 0.25, 1);
    }
    @keyframes slideInUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }

    .beta-icon {
        color: #FF9500;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    .beta-content h2 {
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        color: #1D1D1F;
    }

    .beta-content p {
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #86868B;
        line-height: 1.5;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .beta-actions {
        margin-top: 24px;
    }

    .apple-button.primary {
        background: var(--apple-accent);
        color: white;
        border: none;
        padding: 12px 32px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        font-size: 15px;
        font-weight: 600;
        cursor: pointer;
        width: 100%;
        transition: transform 0.2s, background 0.2s;
    }
    .apple-button.primary:hover {
        background: #0062CC;
        transform: scale(1.02);
    }
    .apple-button.primary:active {
        transform: scale(0.98);
    }
</style>
